&C---------------------======{&WCrimson II NEWS&C}======---------------------&n
 &W June 3, 2019 -
   &w*&n Changed some items at Questmaster. Potions of Bind Souls/Demon
     Flesh have changed and Bow and Crossbow has been improved for Morts.

 &W May 21, 2019 -
   &w*&n Some equipment in HadesCastle and Darkcastle has been rebalanced.
     Development of new Mobs/Zones has begun.
	  
 &W June 5, 2018 -
   &w*&n Winter Wonderland has been removed from Production. It may return 
     for the Holidays

 &W December 01, 2013 -
   &w*&n Zone Update: DragonRealm3 had a mob and items updated. New gear
     has been added to the zone also.

 &W 2010 Summary - 
   &w*&n There have been some updates to the following zones:
     GerinsTower and RealmOfKhorne
   &w*&n New Items and Services at Questmaster. The prices and items are 
     subject to change in availability and price.
   &w*&n Bots are now prohibited on Crimson MUD 2.  If you have questions
     regarding this change see 'help bots'.
   &w*&n The WIPE code has been modified.  Players and kits will still be
     wiped.  Avatars will not be wiped for 12 months. The remaining morts
     have had their wipe time extended. See "help wipe".

 &W January 17, 2009 -
   &w*&n Yay, another code update.  For some of you, the latest version
     will be very apparent.  Among other things, you should notice now
     a reminder to vote for our mud via the MUDCONNECTOR website.  This
     recommendation was made by Bane / Archangel.  Good suggestion!

  &W September 11, 2007 - &n
   &w*&n NewbieVillage and GnomeVillage are now enhanced.  Changes
     include new rooms, new mobs, and new gear.  Both zones should
     be more enjoyable to play for a lower-level mortal.
	   
	   
